sentences.english: All along the disease is considered to be caused by abnormal swim bladders.

sentences.english: But the X-ray photography show is that it is still possible to suffer from the disease and normal swim bladders.
sentences.chinese: 可是X线摄影显示即使鱼鳔正常仍有可能患上该病。

sentences.english: The pressure in the swim bladder is regulated by a gas gland.

sentences.english: Piranhas produce noises by vibrating, or moving their swim bladders.
sentences.chinese: 食人鱼通过震动或者移动它们的鱼鳔来制造声音。
